We provide links to other websites which are not operated and controlled by Dyson. We have no control over and are not responsible for the content of those sites or how the third parties responsible for them collect and use your personal data. We do not endorse or make any representations about third party websites.
Third party websites usually have their own privacy notices explaining how they use and share your personal data. You should carefully review those privacy notices before you use these websites to make sure that you are happy with how your personal data is being collected and shared.
